James F. Small, administrator of the estate of Patricia M. Small, deceased, appellant, v. William H. Stolte, appellee.Gen. No. 30,639.

Taylor, P. J., dissents.

Opinion filed June 23, 1926.Rehearing denied July 12, 1926.Joseph D. Ryan and Craig A. Hood, for appellant; Joseph D. Ryan and Edmund M. Sinnott, of counsel.Kirkland, Patterson & Fleming, for appellee; Weymouth Kirkland, Jay Fred Reeve and William H. Symmes, of counsel. Mr. Justice Thomson

delivered the opinion of the court.
